Played across diverse terrains, from wooded areas to urban landscapes, the objective is simple yet challenging: teams strive to infiltrate the opponent's territory, snatch their flag, and return it safely to their own base, all while defending their own flag from being captured. The game demands a harmonious synergy of stealth, communication, and tactical prowess as players navigate obstacles, employ diversionary tactics, and outsmart adversaries. Fast-paced and dynamic, Capture the Flag immerses participants in a thrilling pursuit where strategy and physical agility intersect. It promotes camaraderie, strategic thinking, and physical fitness, making it a timeless and universally loved classic in the realm of team sports and recreational activities. Question: How to play? 
Answer: Knock out all of the enemy spawns until your team's spawns are the last ones remaining!

Question: What are the tricks to become a pro? 
Answer: To "bomb jump," lay a bomb and jump at the same time. You will go flying upward! To fly a long distance in any direction, you can lay a bomb and ride the explosive force. You can give yourself more air time while falling by using the sword's float when you lunge. You can use a rocket while falling to do a "rocket jump" to preserve your momentum.
